Name: FileName
Description: Name of the file being appended.  May be the name of an active dataframe.

Name: Software
Description: The software package that works with the file.

Name: FileFormat
Description: The name of a file format
Enumeration: csv txt dat xls xlsx sav dta sas7bdat rds rdata

Name: IsCompressed
Description: Indicates whether the file format is compressed.
